{"descriptions":[{"id":1331,"title":null,"content":"\u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eThis construction is used to form verbs from adjectives as follows:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཆེན་པོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Big\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཆེ་རུ་འགྲོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;To grow bigger,\u0026rdquo; \u0026ldquo;to get bigger\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཆེ་རུ་བཏང་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;To make bigger\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཡག་པོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Good\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཡག་རུ་འགྲོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;To get better\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཡག་རུ་བཏང་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;To improve, make better\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eThe past form of \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eརུ་འགྲོ་\u003c/span\u003e is \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eརུ་ཕྱིན་\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eIn Literary Tibetan, the formation of the oblique follows the usual rules:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eརིང་པོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Long\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eརིང་རུ་གཏང་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;To lengthen\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eརིང་དུ་བཏང་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;To lengthen\u0026rdquo; (Literary) \u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཐུང་ཐུང་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Short\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཐུང་རུ་བཏང་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;To shorten\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཐུང་དུ་བཏང་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;To shorten\u0026rdquo; (Literary)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eམགྱོགས་པོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Fast\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eམགྱོགས་རུ་བཏང་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;To accelerate\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eམགྱོགས་སུ་བཏང་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;To accelerate\u0026rdquo; (Literary)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e","source_url":null,"is_primary":true,"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:39 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:39 UTC","authors":[{"id":"6","fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre"}]}]}